6.title: The Garden of Forking Paths
6.content: “I thought of a labyrinth of labyrinths, of one sinuous spreading labyrinth that would encompass the past and the future and in some way involve the stars.” ― Jorge Luis Borges, The Garden of Forking Paths . These pages contain notes and references on random topics that I try to think about beyond my physics. It covers mostly books, art and films. I will also use this space to record some of my writings but the main goal is to capture my thoughts.
